detail.name: Power Pole
detail.effect: [Activate Battle][Your Turn] Your cards that are in a battle get +15000 power for the battle. Then, choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards and it gets -10000 power for the turn.

detail.name: 如意棒
detail.effect: 【起動 戦闘中】【自分のターン中】自分の戦闘中のカードは、この戦闘中、パワー+15000。その後、相手のバトルカード1枚までを選び、このターン中、パワー-10000。
